# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s21_db9b9fbd:

    # Amber "Can you {i}please{/i} keep to the signs?"
    Amber "Может быть ты все-таки {i}будешь{/i} следить за знаками?"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s21_0a08c146:

    # Marina "I will, stop being such a worrywart."
    Marina "Буду, буду, не нуди."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s21_0cf90357:

    # "Marina skips through the sand, gleefully oblivious that her \"trail\" is a badly marked patch of dirt over the plains of the Mojave."
    "Marina salta sobre la arena, alegremente ajena a que su \"sendero\" es un parche de tierra mal señalizado sobre las llanuras del Mojave."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s21_1c11d444:

    # Amber "That’s what you said last time. If you’re not careful, we’re gonna get lost—again."
    Amber "Тоже самое ты говорила в прошлый раз. Если ты не будешь внимательна, мы снова заблудимся."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s21_bf0e0b67:

    # Marina "Aww, you didn’t like those old cabins we found?"
    Marina "Ооо, тебе не понравились те старые домишки, что мы нашли?"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s21_5cab475a:

    # Amber "It gets old after the second time, Mare."
    Amber "После того, как находишь их два раза подряд, они уже не кажутся интересными, Мари."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s21_7426c2da:

    # "It kills daylight, too. The sun has faded to orange, and will soon sink out of view."
    "También mata el día. El sol se ha desvanecido a un tono naranja, y pronto se ocultará de la vista."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s21_f0ba3d61:

    # "There’s no way we’re getting back before dark."
    "No hay manera de que volvamos antes del anochecer."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s21_3f347e77:

    # "But hey, maybe that’s not such a bad thing."
    "Pero bueno, quizás eso no sea tan malo."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s21_019cccd9:

    # "We’ve already found the treasure, so spending some time with Marina is a nice reward."
    "Ya encontramos el tesoro, así que pasar un tiempo con Marina es una linda recompensa."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:96
translate spanish hwb_s21_846a6e09:

    # Marina "So about this Fire Wave thing…"
    Marina "Так на счет этой Огненной Волны…"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s21_b2640c25:

    # Marina "And yes! I know it’s not an ocean of lava, smartypants."
    Marina "И да, я знаю, что речь не про океан из лавы, зазнайка."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s21_fbb0f59c:

    # "Damn. I must be running out of material."
    "Rayos. Debo estar quedándome sin material."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s21_d4eccb54:

    # Marina "I mean, it's so cool - well, hot, I guess - but what is it?"
    Marina "Это классная и, наверное, очень горячая штука.... но что это такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s21_921d6d75:

    # Amber "What's the fire wave? It’s, a uh… windy... thing. That winds around rocks and stuff. And looks like fire."
    Amber "Что такое огненная волна? Это... Это типа ветер, который тут дует среди камней. Ну он выглядит так, будто это огонь."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s21_3698e57e:

    # Amber "At least, I think that’s what it was."
    Amber "По крайней мере, я так думаю."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s21_60bec586:

    # Marina "{cps=10}Ohhhhhhhhhhh?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=10}Оуууу?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:138
translate spanish hwb_s21_1e256ebc:

    # "A devilish grin slinks onto Marina’s face and she attaches herself to me like velcro, nudging my shoulders."
    "Una sonrisa diabólica se desliza en el rostro de Marina y se pega a mí como velcro, empujándome los hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s21_094eb4f2:

    # Marina "You don’t know what it is either, do you?"
    Marina "То есть ты сама не знаешь, что это такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s21_eeab6ea0:

    # Amber "Wh-What? Do so!"
    Amber "Ч-чего? Я знаю!"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s21_2c00de54:

    # "Her grin grows until I force myself to look away."
    "Su sonrisa crece hasta que me obligo a apartar la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s21_12f3da6e:

    # "She’s not gonna get the satisfaction."
    "No va a tener esa satisfacción."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s21_26b92deb:

    # Amber "I’ve seen pictures."
    Amber "Я видела картинки..."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:156
translate spanish hwb_s21_36f7abf9:

    # Marina "Ohhhhh, you’ve seen pictures? What sorta pictures?"
    Marina "Ооооо, ты видела картинки? Какие же?"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:160
translate spanish hwb_s21_8a37bd75:

    # Amber "Y’know. The picture-y kind."
    Amber "Ну знаешь. Фотографические такие."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s21_81018f00:

    # "I can just feel her revelling in this. For the first time, she’s got me playing right into her hands."
    "Puedo sentir cómo se regodea en esto. Por primera vez, me tiene justo donde quiere."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s21_d5bdaba1:

    # Amber "Oh shut up."
    Amber "Ой, все."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s21_fb6ce431:

    # "I feel a slap against my wrist, then a tug. Looking down, I see Marina’s bright dimples shining through her round cheeks."
    "Siento una palmada en mi muñeca, luego un tirón. Al mirar hacia abajo, veo los brillantes hoyuelos de Marina asomando entre sus mejillas redondas."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s21_9ac8638c:

    # Marina "Why don’t we find out together?"
    Marina "Почему бы нам самим не разузнать?"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s21_866e90b4:

    # "I’m stunned."
    "Me quedo atónita."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s21_f19b373b:

    # "It’s a position we’ve been in before, but it’s supposed to be the other way around. I’m always pulling her. That’s my job."
    "Es una posición en la que hemos estado antes, pero se supone que debería ser al revés. Siempre soy yo quien la jala. Ese es mi trabajo."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s21_75a77c69:

    # "But now, it’s her smooth fingers locked around my wrist. {i}Her{/i} fingernails grazing above {i}my{/i} skin."
    "Pero ahora, son sus dedos suaves los que rodean mi muñeca. {i}Sus{/i} uñas rozando sobre {i}mi{/i} piel."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s21_e9310259:

    # "The realization doesn’t even have time to sink in before she propels herself forward, with me in tow."
    "La revelación ni siquiera tiene tiempo de asentarse antes de que ella se lance hacia adelante, conmigo a cuestas."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s21_a529e723:

    # Amber "Hey wait! Hold on!"
    Amber "Стой! Подожди!"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s21_df2ba244:

    # "I kick up sand and grit as I'm practically dragged along by Marina, who meets my yelps with silence."
    "Levanto arena y polvo mientras Marina prácticamente me arrastra, respondiendo a mis gritos con silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s21_cbac1655:

    # "Then she halts as quickly as she took off, leaving me to shoot forward and stumble to a stop."
    "Luego se detiene tan rápido como arrancó, dejándome disparar hacia adelante y tropezar hasta parar."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s21_7a7dd5f9:

    # Amber "Ya could have at least warned me before ya—"
    Amber "Ты бы хоть предупредила перед тем как—"

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s21_6c00d211:

    # "I go silent."
    "Me quedo en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s21_d06b3480:

    # "Marina does, too."
    "Marina también."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s21_0d870c84:

    # "The Fire Wave."
    "La Ola de Fuego."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s21_0ce32cf3:

    # "Swirling ribbons of red wrap around the hillside and stretch out to the horizon. The setting sun casts light and shadow across the ground and sky, shading it all with intense golds, pinks, and purples."
    "Cintas arremolinadas de rojo envuelven la ladera y se extienden hasta el horizonte. El sol poniente proyecta luz y sombra sobre el suelo y el cielo, tiñéndolo todo con intensos dorados, rosas y púrpuras."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s21_19bcef61:

    # "As the sky dims, a shred of stray light passes over the shade and shines directly on us."
    "Mientras el cielo se oscurece, un destello de luz perdida cruza la sombra y brilla directamente sobre nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s21_9a189f10:

    # "Directly on Marina."
    "Directamente sobre Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:254
translate spanish hwb_s21_acab5855:

    # "She stares on, silent."
    "Ella mira, en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s21_7cf4f5c1:

    # "I can feel every glint of emotion coming from her."
    "Puedo sentir cada destello de emoción que emana de ella."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s21_5a28f027:

    # "Every breath taken away."
    "Cada respiración contenida."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s21_8bfb770d:

    # "Every raw feeling that builds up inside her, only to be choked back down."
    "Cada sentimiento crudo que se acumula dentro de ella, solo para ser ahogado de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s21_99106297:

    # "All of it."
    "Todo eso."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s21_12bd5137:

    # "I glance between her and the scene stretched out before us. The pockets of sky with their deep, vivid colors are beautiful, but the choice is easy."
    "Miro entre ella y la escena que se extiende ante nosotros. Los retazos de cielo con sus colores profundos y vívidos son hermosos, pero la elección es fácil."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s21_7767377c:

    # "I fixate on Marina."
    "Me fijo en Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s21_ef688f18:

    # "Her clear, sweet blue eyes."
    "Sus claros y dulces ojos azules."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s21_96338b46:

    # "Her cute, round cheeks."
    "Sus lindas y redondas mejillas."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s21_dad8e56d:

    # "Her lips, as they quiver ever so slightly."
    "Sus labios, mientras tiemblan ligeramente."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s21_8244f6d8:

    # "Laying a hand on her shoulder, I turn her towards me and softly touch her cheek."
    "Poniendo una mano en su hombro, la giro hacia mí y toco suavemente su mejilla."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s21_33fad5ea:

    # "Her mouth slips open with a faint gasp, but all it takes is a gentle stroke of her face for that uncertainty to be wiped away."
    "Su boca se entreabre con un leve jadeo, pero basta una caricia suave en su rostro para que esa incertidumbre se desvanezca."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s21_eb08051e:

    # "Marina holds my gaze. My eyes relax and I step closer, so I can feel the warmth of her body against mine."
    "Marina sostiene mi mirada. Mis ojos se relajan y me acerco, para sentir el calor de su cuerpo contra el mío."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:280
translate spanish hwb_s21_227d07c8:

    # "Then, I lean in and press my lips to hers."
    "Luego, me inclino y presiono mis labios contra los suyos."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s21_f9789def:

    # "So soft."
    "Tan suaves."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s21_61970aa9:

    # "I keep myself pressed against her, letting my lips move with the natural flow."
    "Me mantengo presionada contra ella, dejando que mis labios se muevan con el flujo natural."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s21_7783425e:

    # "But she doesn’t press back."
    "Pero ella no responde al beso."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s21_fc08ebac:

    # "Afraid, I pull away, but before I can step back, she pulls me closer and lets her lips melt into mine."
    "Asustada, me aparto, pero antes de que pueda retroceder, ella me atrae más cerca y deja que sus labios se fundan con los míos."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s21_e15f73fc:

    # "I let the pattern take control. Our mouths move inside each other, full of tender caution as we ease in."
    "Dejo que el ritmo tome el control. Nuestras bocas se mueven una dentro de la otra, llenas de tierna cautela mientras nos soltamos."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s21_58421fca:

    # "We repeat the process infinitely. Bathed in the light of sunset, the two of us exchange ‘something’."
    "Repetimos el proceso infinitamente. Bañadas por la luz del atardecer, las dos intercambiamos 'algo'."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s21_f7840c4b:

    # "I eventually pull back, unsure of what to say, and scared of what I could."
    "Finalmente me aparto, sin saber qué decir, y asustada de lo que podría decir."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s21_78249793:

    # "We turn back to find the last rays of sunlight slipping behind the sand."
    "Nos giramos para ver los últimos rayos de sol deslizándose tras la arena."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s21_5fe40c71:

    # "Something brushes against my hand, tickling for a moment before intertwining between my fingers."
    "Algo roza mi mano, cosquilleando por un momento antes de entrelazarse entre mis dedos."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s21_e1a85f64:

    # "Her grip is loose, but I wrap my fingers around so that I'm holding her firmly."
    "Su agarre es flojo, pero envuelvo mis dedos alrededor para sostenerla firmemente."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s21_b6b65f6f:

    # "We watch the last of the light drift into a peaceful evening."
    "Vemos cómo la última luz se desvanece en una tarde tranquila."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s21_843be388:

    # "Together."
    "Juntas."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s21_22a3f02e:

    # Marina "It’s pretty."
    Marina "Это прекрасно."

# game/script/hwb_s21.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s21_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Ага."

